<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto p-3 md:p-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-lime-50 via-white to-green-50 rounded-3xl shadow-xl" data-controller="exercise-checker">

  <!-- Header -->
  <div class="mb-8">
    <div class="flex items-start sm:items-center justify-between gap-4 mb-4">
      <div class="flex flex-col-reverse sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center gap-2 sm:gap-4">
        <div class="bg-lime-500 text-white text-md sm:text-xl px-2 sm:px-4 py-1.5 sm:py-2 rounded-lg font-bold">
          MORFOLOGIA
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-lime-600">Aggettivi e pronomi indefiniti</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="flex-shrink-0 bg-red-600 text-white rounded-full w-10 h-10 sm:w-12 sm:h-12 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg sm:text-xl">
        58
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Info Box with Illustration -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-100 to-amber-100 rounded-2xl border-4 border-yellow-300 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4">
      <div>
        <%= image_tag "nvl5_gram_p058_immagine01.jpg", alt: "Illustrazione indefiniti", class: "w-full rounded-lg shadow-lg mb-4" %>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 mb-3">
          Gli <strong>indefiniti</strong> indicano in modo non preciso qualcosa o qualcuno oppure una quantità generica.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-red-600 font-bold">•</span>
            <span>Gli <strong class="text-red-600">aggettivi indefiniti</strong> accompagnano il nome → <strong>alcune</strong> regole, <strong>ciascun</strong> visitatore, <strong>qualche</strong> domanda;</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold">•</span>
            <span>I <strong class="text-blue-600">pronomi indefiniti</strong> sostituiscono il nome → <strong>ognuno</strong> resti..., <strong>qualcuno</strong> ha....</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Attention Box -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-100 to-red-100 rounded-xl border-3 border-orange-400 p-4">
    <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-800">
      <strong class="text-orange-700">Attenzione!</strong> Alcuni indefiniti sono <strong class="text-red-600">solo aggettivi</strong>,
      altri sono <strong class="text-blue-600">solo pronomi</strong>, altri ancora sono <strong class="text-purple-600">sia aggettivi sia pronomi</strong>. Osserva.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Table of indefinites -->
  <div class="mb-6 overflow-x-auto">
    <table class="w-full border-collapse text-sm md:text-base">
      <thead>
        <tr class="bg-gradient-to-r from-red-100 to-blue-100">
          <th class="border-3 border-gray-300 px-4 py-3 text-red-700 font-bold">Solo aggettivi indefiniti</th>
          <th class="border-3 border-gray-300 px-4 py-3 text-blue-700 font-bold">Solo pronomi indefiniti</th>
          <th class="border-3 border-gray-300 px-4 py-3 text-purple-700 font-bold">Aggettivi e pronomi indefiniti</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td class="border-2 border-gray-300 px-4 py-6 text-center bg-red-50">
            <p class="font-semibold">qualche • ogni</p>
            <p class="font-semibold">qualunque • qualsiasi</p>
          </td>
          <td class="border-2 border-gray-300 px-4 py-6 text-center bg-blue-50">
            <p class="font-semibold">uno / una • qualcuno • qualcosa</p>
            <p class="font-semibold">ognuno • nulla</p>
            <p class="font-semibold">niente • chiunque</p>
          </td>
          <td class="border-2 border-gray-300 px-4 py-6 text-center bg-purple-50">
            <p class="font-semibold">alcuno • certo • nessuno • molto</p>
            <p class="font-semibold">poco • parecchio • troppo • tanto</p>
            <p class="font-semibold">altro • ciascuno • tutto • tale</p>
            <p class="font-semibold">altrettanto</p>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 1: IMPARARE TUTTI -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-100 to-amber-100 rounded-2xl border-4 border-yellow-300 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6" data-controller="word-highlighter" data-word-highlighter-multi-color-value="false">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-blue-700 mb-4 flex items-center flex-wrap gap-2">
      <span class="bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center">1</span>
      <span class="bg-yellow-400 text-blue-900 px-3 py-1 rounded-lg font-bold">IMPARARE TUTTI</span>
      <span>Clicca sugli aggettivi indefiniti <span class="inline-block w-4 h-4 bg-red-300 rounded ml-1 align-middle"></span></span>
    </h2>

    <!-- Color Selector (hidden for mono-color) -->
    <div class="hidden">
      <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-red-300"
           data-word-highlighter-target="colorBox"
           data-color="red">
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-base md:text-lg cursor-pointer">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 space-y-3">
        <p class="text-gray-700">• Ho invitato <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="red">molti</span> <u>amici</u> al mio compleanno.</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">• Vado a scuola <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="red">tutti</span> i <u>giorni</u> con la bicicletta.</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">• Quest'auto dà <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="red">troppi</span> <u>problemi</u>, dobbiamo sostituirla.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 space-y-3">
        <p class="text-gray-700">• <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="red">Ciascun</span> <u>giocatore</u> deve conoscere le regole.</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">• Ci sarà un'<span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="red">altra</span> <u>occasione</u> per la tua squadra.</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">• <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="red">Nessun</span> <u>essere umano</u> ha mai battuto Alpha Go agli scacchi.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Reference -->
  <div class="mt-6 text-center">
    <p class="text-red-600 font-bold text-base md:text-lg">Esercizi p. <%= link_to "159", pagina_path("nvl5_gram_p159"), class: "text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-800 underline" %> e <%= link_to "163", pagina_path("nvl5_gram_p163"), class: "text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-800 underline" %></p>
  </div>

  <%= render partial: "shared/exercise_controls" %>

</div>
